membership:
EUROMIL is participating in the Fundamental Rights Platform (FRP) of the EU Agency for Fundamental Rights (FRA).&#xd;
The organisation has participatory status with the Council of Europe (CoE) and consultative status with the UN Economic and Social Council (ECOSOC). &#xd;
EUROMIL also maintains contacts with the North Atlantic Treaty Organization Parliamentary Assembly (NATO PA) and the Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe (OSCE).&#xd;
Additionally, EUROMIL is a member of the European Movement International (EMI), Friends of Europe and the Kangaroo Group.

